ments/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5148:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1119587\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png\" alt=\"compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png 568w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-150x42.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-300x84.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /><br />\nToday we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible WooCommerce extensions.</p>\n<p>The WooCommerce extensions are:¬†<a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-custom-fields-product-addons/11332742\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce Custom Fields &amp; Product Add-ons</a>, <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-order-status-manager/\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce Order Status Manager</a>, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-role-based-pricing-pro/14120734\" target=\"_blank\">Woocommerce Role Based Price</a>, <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/print-invoices-packing-lists/\" target=\"_blank\">Print Invoices &amp; Packing lists</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you‚Äôre a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and are ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our¬†<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Custom Fields &amp; Product Add-ons</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce Custom Fields &amp; Product Add-ons allows you to create custom product, checkout, order and user fields, provide and gather additional information in a structured way, and sell configurable products, product add-ons and extra product options.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-custom-fields-product-addons/11332742\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce Custom Fields &amp; Product Add-ons</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Order Status Manager</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Create, edit, and delete completely custom order statuses and integrate them seamlessly into your order management flow.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-order-status-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase WooCommerce Order Status Manager</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Woocommerce Role Based Price</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin extends WooCommerce so that products can be offered at different prices for different customer groups.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/woocommerce-role-based-pricing-pro/14120734\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Woocommerce Role Based Price</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Print Invoices &amp; Packing lists</h2>\n<blockquote><p>The WooCommerce Print Invoice &amp; Packing list extension is the a tool to handle invoices, packing lists, and pick lists in your WooCommerce store.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/print-invoices-packing-lists/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Print Invoices &amp; Packing lists</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EL3-nKfESxQ:BZeg-b2nLXM:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EL3-nKfESxQ:BZeg-b2nLXM:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EL3-nKfESxQ:BZeg-b2nLXM:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EL3-nKfESxQ:BZeg-b2nLXM:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=EL3-nKfESxQ:BZeg-b2nLXM:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=EL3-nKfESxQ:BZeg-b2nLXM:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/EL3-nKfESxQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://wpml.org/2017/01/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-jan-2017/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";