Templates Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://facetwp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">FacetWP</a>, <a href=\"https://www.mapsmarker.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maps Marker Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/nextbuzz/buzz-seo\" target=\"_blank\">Buzz SEO</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you‚Äôre a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our¬†<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Salon Booking</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Salon Booking is a complete and easy to manage appointments booking system to help your business getting more reservations on your website and saving a lot of time with your agenda management tasks.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/salon-booking-wordpress-plugin/15963435\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Salon Booking</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Maintenance Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Maintenance PRO is packed with advanced features, for a powerful and effective maintenance mode splash page</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/maintenance-pro-wordpress-plugin/2781350\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Maintenance Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Post Custom Templates Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Create custom post templates easily</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/post-custom-templates-pro-wordpress-plugin/18029807\" target=\"_blank\">download Post Custom Templates Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">FacetWP</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Plugin for Advanced Filtering for WordPress</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://facetwp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase FacetWP</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Maps Marker Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Display locations and routes on your WordPress single site or MultiSite installation.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.mapsmarker.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Maps Marker Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Buzz SEO</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Buzz SEO is a WordPress SEO plugin. It covers the basics of SEO optimization.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://github.com/nextbuzz/buzz-seo\" target=\"_blank\">Download Buzz SEO</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=c-sPNT5YcUk:ZbDdf_Kxvqc:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=c-sPNT5YcUk:ZbDdf_Kxvqc:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=c-sPNT5YcUk:ZbDdf_Kx